---
import BookingWidget from './BookingWidget.tsx'
---

<section class="hero" id="top">
  <div class="hero-bg">
    <img
      src="https://archibald-ouramdane.fr/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/archibald-ouramdane-therapie-manuelle-des-fascias-soin-calme-et-bien-etre-bis-scaled.jpg"
      alt="Personne allongée et détendue lors d'un soin de thérapie manuelle des fascias, dans une ambiance calme et apaisante au cabinet de Marseille"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <span class="stars" aria-hidden="true">★★★★★</span>
        <span class="t-text"><b>69 avis</b> · 5/5 sur Google</span>
      </div>
      <h1>Relâcher les tensions,<br /><em>retrouver le sommeil</em><br />et apaiser la douleur.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        À Marseille, j'accompagne en douceur les personnes confrontées au stress, aux insomnies et
        aux douleurs chroniques, par un travail manuel des fascias, respectueux du rythme de chacun.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" data-scroll-book>Réserver ma séance</button>
        <a class="hero-call" href="tel:0688468367">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.13.96.36 1.9.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.9.34 1.85.57 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"/></svg>
          06 88 46 83 67
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <span><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="9"/><path d="M12 7v5l3 2"/></svg>Séance ≈ 75 min</span>
        <span><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 10c0 6-9 12-9 12s-9-6-9-12a9 9 0 0 1 18 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>Cabinet & domicile</span>
        <span><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6 9 17l-5-5"/></svg>107 Cours Lieutaud · 13006</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <BookingWidget client:load />
  </div>
</section>
